Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花 你為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:43.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個請求 亞爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:52.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 亞爾特一直帶著的紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能教我怎麼折嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:14.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問件事可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾特為什麼想去天空飛行？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:21.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:30.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母親體弱多病 總是看著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:36.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時母親說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:41.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:49.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湛藍 無邊無際的地平線和白雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:54.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣真正的自由的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像童話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對出生在這艘船上的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:11.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:33.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓它飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:44.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:09.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都…希望自由地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:11.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:16.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:20.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:21.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 亞爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可是Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它們殺了米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:34.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它才剛蛻皮沒做過任何壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也要殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有Vajra在
